144|title=Maximum Reviews - Saturn: Worms - Lemmings with guns!|magazine=Maximum: The Video Game Magazine|issue=3|publisher=[[Emap International Limited]]|date=January 1996|page=144}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[Mean Machines#Mean Machines Sega and Nintendo Magazine System|Mean Machines Sega]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 79/100<ref name=\"MMSSMDw\">{{cite magazine|author1=Marcus|author2=Gus|url=https://archive.org/stream/mean-machines-sega-magazine-46#page/n63/mode/2up|title=Megadrive Review - Worms|magazine=[[Mean Machines#Mean Machines Sega and Nintendo Magazine System|Mean Machines Sega]]|issue=46|publisher=[[Ascential|EMAP]]|date=August 1996|pages=64-65}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 87/100<ref name=\"MMSSSw\">{{cite magazine|author1=Steve|author2=Marcus|url=https://archive.org/stream/mean-machines-sega-magazine-40#page/n67/mode/2up|title=Saturn Review - Worms|magazine=[[Mean Machines#Mean Machines Sega and Nintendo Magazine System|Mean Machines Sega]]|issue=40|publisher=[[Ascential|EMAP]]|date=February 1996|pages=68-70}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:fr:Mega Force|Mega Force]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 90%<ref name=\"MForceSMDw\">{{cite magazine|author=Francis|url=https://www.abandonware-magazines.org/affiche_mag.php?mag=40&num=5058&album=oui|title=Zapping - Worms (Megadrive Europ\u00e9enne)|magazine=[[:fr:Mega Force|Mega Force]]|issue=48|publisher=MegaPress, S.A.R.L.|date=March 1996|pages=84-86|lang=fr}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 92%<ref name=\"MForceSSw\">{{cite magazine|author=Laurent|url=https://www.abandonware-magazines.org/affiche_mag.php?mag=40&num=5055&album=oui|title=Zapping - Worms (Saturn Europ\u00e9enne)|magazine=[[:fr:Mega Force|Mega Force]]|issue=45|publisher=MegaPress, S.A.R.L.|date=December 1995|pages=84-87|lang=fr}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:Mega Fun|Mega Fun]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 87%<ref name=\"MFSMDPSw\">{{cite magazine|last1=Schneider|first1=Ulf|last2=Kraft|