#Official UK PlayStation Magazine|Official UK PlayStation Magazine]]|issue=2|publisher=[[Future plc|Future Publishing]]|date=January 1996|page=107}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[The One (magazine)#History|The One for Amiga Games]]''\n| 94%<ref name=\"TOfAGA500w\">{{cite magazine|last=|first=|url=https://archive.org/stream/theone-magazine-87#page/n15/mode/2up|title=Review - Worms|magazine=[[The One (magazine)#History|The One for Amiga Games]]|issue=87|publisher=[[Ascential|EMAP]]|date=Christmas 1996|pages=16\u201319}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:PC Games|PC Games]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 84%<ref name=\"PCGamesPCw\">{{cite magazine|last=Aichinger|first=Herbert|url=https://archive.org/stream/pcgamesmagazine-1996-02#page/n123/mode/2up|title=Review: Worms - Wurmsketch|magazine=[[:de:PC Games|PC Games]]|issue=41|publisher=[[:de:Computec Media Group|CT Computec Verlag GmbH & Co. KG]]|date=February 1996|pages=124-125|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:PC Joker|PC Joker]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 87%<ref name=\"PCJokerPCw\">{{cite magazine|last=Magenauer|first=Max|url=https://www.kultboy.com/index.php?site=t&id=11814|title=Twilight \u2014 Games F\u00fcr Individualisten: Worms - Da ist der Wurm drin!|magazine=[[:de:PC Joker|PC Joker]]|issue=37|publisher=Joker-Verlag|date=December 1995|pages=78-79|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n| ''[[:de:PC Player|PC Player]]''\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| 69/100<ref name=\"PCPlayerPCw\">{{cite magazine|last=Lenhardt|first=Heinrich|url=https://www.kultboy.com/index.php?site=t&id=12228|title=Spiele-test - Worms|magazine=[[:de:PC Player|PC Player]]|issue=36|publisher=[[:de:Future plc|Future Verlag]]|date=December 1995|pages=108-109|lang=de}}</ref>\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\